window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>In this latest adrenaline-charged thriller from number one </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> best-selling author Stuart Woods, Stone Barrington takes on a vengeful rival.</b></p> <p>Stone&nbsp;Barrington is looking forward to some quiet time in New York City, until he is asked to transport precious, top-secret cargo across the Atlantic. Taking on the challenge, Stone flies off unaware of what - or who - he is bringing with him.&nbsp;</p> <p>But his plans to lie low are quickly spoiled when a dangerous dispatcher tracks down Stone and his tantalizing mystery guest, intent on payback - and silencing anyone who poses a threat. From the English countryside to the balmy beaches of Key West, Stone is on an international mission to hide and protect those closest to him.</p>"; 
